\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\fs28 Game Concept: Slime Empire\fs22\par
\b Slime Empire \b0 is an open-world RTS empire-building game where players build relationships between generals, clans, and units to establish and expand their domain. Players capture spawn points, recruit slime units, promote worthy units to generals, and balance military conquest with diplomacy and resource management.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qc\fs28 PLAYER EXPERIENCE & GAMEPLAY LOOP\fs22\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs24 Core Experience\b0\fs22\par
Slime Empire offers players the experience of building and managing their own empire in a cute, slime-filled world. Players should feel like rulers making meaningful strategic decisions that shape their domain according to their preferred playstyle - whether through conquest, diplomacy, or economic development.\par
\b\fs24 Moment-to-Moment Gameplay\b0\fs22\par
The player's experience flows seamlessly between exploration, combat, and management:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Exploration Phase: Players navigate the fog of war to discover new territories, scout for unclaimed spawn points and resources, and encounter other clans\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Expansion Phase: Capturing spawn points to extend territory, producing new units, and developing provinces\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Interaction Phase: Engaging in combat, conducting diplomacy, and managing relationships between generals\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs24 Strategic Decision Making\b0\fs22\par
Players constantly make decisions that shape their empire:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Military Decisions: Which spawn points to capture? When to promote units to generals? How to compose armies?\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Diplomatic Decisions: Which clans to befriend? When to declare war? Which princesses to pursue?\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Economic Decisions: Which resources to prioritize? How to allocate resources?\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs24 Relationship-Driven Gameplay\b0\fs22\par
The relationship system creates emergent storytelling opportunities:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 A general might develop interest in a princess, prompting diplomatic or military approaches\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Generals with strong relationships might influence diplomatic options\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Players can role-play based on developing relationships between characters\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs24 Open-Ended Progression\b0\fs22\par
Unlike games with strict victory conditions, Slime Empire emphasizes the journey of building an empire:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 No forced end-game, allowing players to continue expanding indefinitely\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Multiple viable strategies for growth and dominance\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Freedom to change approach based on emerging situations\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs24 Seamless World Interaction\b0\fs22\par
All gameplay happens on a single, continuous world map:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Battles occur in real-time directly on the world map without separate battle screens\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Cultural influence visibly spreads across territories\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Resource gathering, diplomacy, and combat all take place in the same space\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs24 Supported Playstyles\b0\fs22\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 The Conqueror: Focus on military strength and capturing territory by force\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}The Diplomat: Build positive relationships and form alliances through marriages\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}The Builder: Focus on economic development and resource production\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}The Balanced Ruler: Maintain a mix of military, diplomatic, and economic approaches\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qc\fs28 Core Gameplay Elements\fs22\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs24 Empire Building\b0\fs22\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Players start with a single general and must claim spawn points to expand\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Each spawn point provides resources and the ability to generate new units\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Players develop provinces over time to increase production and unit quality\par

