\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Souls: Captured from defeated enemies, used for special upgrades and eventually "dark path" gameplay\par
