{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}General abilities and relationships influence combat effectiveness\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\par
\fs28 Visual & Audio Style\fs22\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Cute, approachable art style centered on slime characters\par
